# Apple Menu
################################################################################

Menu Apple, Icon apple.xpm, Stick
"About This Computer..." NonSelect, Gray, Action About
"" NonSelect
"Terminal"	Icon mini-display.xpm, Action Exec "xterm" exec xterm
